Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:16.24,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,I lift my eyes a little and look into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:19.28,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,All I do is mutter every time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:24.42,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,I turn my back on this perfect everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:28.12,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Where am I supposed to go
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:33.52,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,With you who are giving me a look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:39.33,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Shadows on back streets
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:43.07,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Hands of a clock
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:49.56,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Repaint the time that has been stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:57.28,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Extended hands, puzzle pieces that don't fit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:06.22,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Until the abandoned two reunite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:10.53,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Something that has been lost
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.53,0:01:18.80,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Recover the last piece
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.24,0:01:24.64,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:36.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,None of us are bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:39.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mizuguchi from the basketball team or me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:42.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or you, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:46.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are no bad people anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:50.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But bad things happen to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:53.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:55.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it a conspiracy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:57.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:01.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Some enormous organization has been\nplotting evil conspiracies against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:03.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:07.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard it through the grapevine the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:15.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai, today's the last day you'll\ncome to this club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:28.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frx10\fry32\frz263.732\fscx56.25\fscy52.5\pos(118,97)\c&H000706&\3c&H444B45&\4c&H444B45&}3 years in the country
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:28.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frx10\fry32\frz263.732\fscx56.25\fscy52.5\c&H000706&\3c&H444B45&\4c&H444B45&\pos(70,84)}3 days in the city
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:32.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frx10\fry32\frz70.59\fscx58.75\fscy51.25\c&H55554E&\4c&HFFFFF9&\3c&HFFFFF9&\pos(78,152)}Graduation Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:32.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frx10\fry32\fscx58.75\fscy51.25\c&H55554E&\4c&HFFFFF9&\3c&HFFFFF9&\frz67.064\pos(53,144)}Sapporo Chuo High School
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:46.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've played cards with me for\nthe last two years, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been four years, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:16.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Four years and four months, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:18.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't look so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:22.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:24.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't I give you some medicine or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:27.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Medicine, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:30.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's mood-altering medicine. You'll feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:35.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you've been suffering from lack of sleep,\NI recommend sleeping pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:38.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if you're depressed, take an antidepressant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:40.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And this one is a mood-stabilizing medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:41.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:44.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai, how many doctors do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:46.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Three right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:54.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Being a working adult is tough, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Being a student preparing for a\ncollege exam is tough, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:03.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing now, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:05.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Working at a ward office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:08.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you work for the government?\NThat's pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:10.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about you, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:17.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Apparently you've got time to wander around on a\nweekday carrying all that stuff with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A part-time worker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wish I was a part-time worker...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:26.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know how to put it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:27.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I'm, err...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:30.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:31.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And inside of the bag, I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:32.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frz104.756\pos(112,132)\fscx70\fscy65\c&H97758A&\3c&H9AAEB8&\4c&H9AAEB8&}Haruka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:32.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,\NAnd inside of the bag, I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:32.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:33.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:34.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ero games!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Figurines!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:37.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,DVDs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:40.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And all kinds of miscellaneous\nanime-related products!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm a typical otaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:44.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I spent all my money for next\nmonth's rent on these!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:46.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm like, '"what am I gonna do now," you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:51.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've already been hikikomori for four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:54.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Call me the Master of Hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:05:00.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Actually, I'd already kind of guessed that\nthat's what you're like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't believe that's what your opinion of me was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:07.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I was only half serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:12.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you know, I still think about it\nevery now and then,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:15.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,about my junior in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:15.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fscx36.25\fscy57.5\frz39.85\frx24\fry324\c&H132F5C&\4c&H021738&\3c&H021738&\move(176,95,176,114,0,2810)}Literature Club
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:19.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He'd tell me about his buddies a lot, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:25.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I never saw anyone come visit\nhim at the club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:32.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can still picture that image clearly in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:37.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We should've made it more official and\ndated each other back then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:42.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We probably had better things to do than just\nplaying cards every single day, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:49.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we would've had a healthy romantic relationship,\nmaybe you never would've become hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:51.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:00.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everything is a conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see, that's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:20.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:23.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please come check it out inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that your cell phone, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:35.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fscx48.75\fscy67.5\pos(249,222)\c&HB4B5AC&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&}Yamazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:35.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fscx48.75\fscy67.5\c&HB4B5AC&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(241,251)}0 sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:38.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where the hell are you, Sato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:40.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been calling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:42.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you at the same spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:44.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you take too much longer, I'm just gonna\nhead back without you! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:47.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Man, he's scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:57.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you still remember that time,\nright before you graduated,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,when I rescued that middle school kid\nwho was being bullied?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:03.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now he's living in the apartment right next to mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:06.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And today, he brought me here with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:10.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Otherwise, a hikikomori guy like me wouldn't be\nwandering around in a place like this, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:15.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me your cell phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:18.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:20.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:25.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Tatsuhiro Sato, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:26.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you remember my first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:29.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fscx48.75\fscy67.5\c&HB4B5AC&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(238,102)}Kashiwa, hi
