Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:31.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fscx48.75\fscy67.5\c&HB4B5AC&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(238,102)}Kashiwa, Hitomi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:35.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now I can contact you any time I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:38.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How convenient things have become, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:44.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you go to a convenience store you can\nbuy food, drinks, cosmetics,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,even cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:51.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But they don't sell relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:00.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can I see you again?
