Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:08.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\frx14\fry328\c&H508AFF&\3c&HFBFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\frz5.731\pos(215,164)\fscx46.25\fscy70}How to Win at Job Interviews
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:08.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was totally lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:08.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was totally lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:11.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who'd have thought that I'd find\nso much Pururin stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:15.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,at some store I happened to stop by\nwhile looking for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And it's all rare stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:20.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if someone who actually worked\non the show sold all the stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:24.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's make use of the blessings received\non today's pilgrimage to the Holy Land
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:27.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and get our noses to the grindstone\nmaking that game!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:30.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Seriously, the Holy Land is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can feel my inspiration flowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:35.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:41.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right, you're hikikomori, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:48.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:52.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you're hikikomori, right, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something hit me when I was in the Holy Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From now on the freckles are in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Characters with freckles are coming at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:05.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:09.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can totally finish it up before\nthe production deadline, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:13.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ten days until the deadline...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:17.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Any game made in ten days time\nisn't going to be much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:22.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if I give it to Misaki\nmy promise to her will be fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:28.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She would never bother me again,\nand I'd go back to my hikikomori life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:32.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:35.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're hikikomori, right, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:41.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato... Sato... Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:46.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The only problem left is your script!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:49.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you just start doing little bits of it and then give\nthem to me as you go, I could manage to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:09.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's thinking I'm pretty weird even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:13.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You wanna know how to get out\nof hikikomori, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:19.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll tell you once you sign the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:22.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe it's really possible that she could...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This could be your last chance, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:29.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sign this and bring it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:38.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The appointment is ten days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:42.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe it's pointless for me to wait on her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:48.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if she really is the goddess\nwho appeared to rescue me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:10:59.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She really came!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:20.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:23.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You still have ten days till the appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:26.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you bring the game by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:31.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, the e.g. I was making has been cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:35.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Making? I thought you said you were going to\nbring the one that you made in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:39.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I meant, the one that I'm working on\nis about to be cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:41.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:43.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By the way, what is "e.g."?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:45.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's short for EROA and GARIOA!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:49.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Essentially, EROA stands for,\N"Economic Rehabilitation in Occupied Area Fund"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:52.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and GARIOA for,\N"Government and Relief in Occupied Areas."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After World War II, America provided funding
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:58.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in order to prevent social unrest\ncaused by illness and starvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:01.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does a game like that really sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:03.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a big lie, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your being a creator was a lie too, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:10.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The truth is that you're unemployed\nand hikikomori, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a deal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:35.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now you're going to be fine, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:38.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With a little training, you'll be able to get out\ninto that big world out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:43.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:48.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A kindhearted girl who rescues\nyoung people who are suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:54.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're going to start your counseling tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:56.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't skip it no matter what, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:03.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you break the promise, you'll have to\npay me a million yen as a penalty!
