Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:55.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fscx53.75\fscy56.25\pos(193,158)\frz9.194}Yamazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd better apologize to Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:04.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I bet he's pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,DON'T GIVE ME THAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's pissed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:09.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's very pissed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:11.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How did this conversation come to that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:15.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First of all, I moved here with the money I made!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:18.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't have to follow your orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is he talking to his parents or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:20.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? That's none of your business!\NIs he talking to his parents or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:22.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen, I will not take over your farm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:25.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen, I will not take over your farm!\NI guess he has his own problems too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:25.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess he has his own problems too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:04.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:06.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:14.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:19.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I'd like to commence the first seminar on\N"How to Get Out of the Hikikomori Condition."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First, a general overview on what\nit is to be hikikomori...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:27.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:27.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0\pos(173,66)\frz24.341}SECRET NOTES
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:33.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Secret notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:36.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like I said, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Secret notes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:41.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not what I'm asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:43.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you can't look, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:44.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:52.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Moving on... What are the causes of hikikomori?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:54.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Based on the results of my research,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:58.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,hikikomori can arise from incompatibility\nwith one's environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:04.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In other words, it's a type of mental problem,\ncaused by an inability to function in society.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:10.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is why it is important to know how\nto come to terms with society.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:12.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:14.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:15.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HA8FFFF&\bord0.5\shad0\fscx250\fscy422.5\pos(193,75)}GOD
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since time immemorial,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:21.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and dissatisfactions with the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:25.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and controlling their emotions\nby believing in and worshipping gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:28.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And for that reason there are\nmany different gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:32.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is said that there are as many as\neight million gods in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:36.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Eight million? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:39.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that just too many, don't\nyou think? Eight million...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:43.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that supposed to be "countless gods"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:48.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fnSegoe Print\bord0\shad0\c&H211E0E&\frz12.775\fscx262.5\fscy233.75\pos(184,109)}Eight million gods
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:48.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's spelled "eight million"\nbut it really means "countless."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ah! I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So there are countless gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:56.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So basically, there are so many gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:16:59.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ahem...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:05.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Many people are saved from their pain\nand suffering thanks to these gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:07.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, that's not the case for some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:10.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those people seek salvation\nin stuff like "philosophy."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:15.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now! I know this is sudden,\nbut let's psychoanalyze you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:20.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\pos(71,56)\c&H898884&\3c&H000100&\shad0\frz3.715}Illustrated!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:20.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H898884&\3c&H000100&\shad0\frz4.404\pos(75,85)}Fascinating
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:20.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H898884&\3c&H000100&\shad0\pos(90,104)\frz4.199}Psychoanalysis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:20.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H898884&\3c&H000100&\shad0\frz3.579\pos(92,132)}by DR. FREUD
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:17.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A guy name Freud came up with this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:20.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and supposedly it became very popular\naround the 19th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:25.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure all that scholarly stuff from earlier\nwas too difficult for you to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:27.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,since you're a college-dropout and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:29.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:31.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But this part is easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:35.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your problem will disappear by talking about\nthe dream you had this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:39.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll analyze it for you, so please explain\nwhat happened in the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:41.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:44.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does she think I don't even know who Freud is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:50.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If that's what she thinks, she can\nanalyze to her heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:53.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There was an enormous and rough-Iooking snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:03.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The snake went under the water,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I thrust a huge sword into an apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shot off a beautiful shiny black gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:17.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Snake... Ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:20.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Apple... Sword... Gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:27.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're done with Freud!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:29.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next is Jung!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:31.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, forget about Jung.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:34.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about the results of the dream analysis?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:39.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HAE3C3A&\3c&HA8A49B&\shad0\frz274.873\pos(92,89)}Easy to Understand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:39.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HAE3C3A&\3c&HA8A49B&\shad0\frz276.296\pos(42,119)}JUNG
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:36.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jung!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:40.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Supposedly this guy had a disagreement with Freud\nand struck out in another direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:43.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like I said! What about the rough-looking snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:46.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about the sword? What about the gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:49.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do they symbolize?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:53.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to hear that from you, Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:55.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:57.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like I said it's time for Jung right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:19:01.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you can't listen to me, then today's\nseminar ends right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:04.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're going to do the rest tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:13.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting much from it anyway, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:20.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh well, I guess I'll stick around for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:23.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,since a breach of contract means\na million yen penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:31.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're hikikomori, right, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:41.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is reason for which I'm thankful\nto have met Misaki though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:48.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've realized something as I talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:48.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0\fnCourier New\fscx65\fscy65\pos(147,213)}Scenario-01.txt
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:49.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fnCordia New\fscx167.5\fscy223.75\pos(302,93)}Scenario-01.txt
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:52.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if I seclude myself in my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:56.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,as long as I'm doing something with\na goal in mind, I'm not hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:09.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\alpha&H40&\c&HF9F94A&}A magical girl of dreams and hopes, dreams and hopes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:07.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's open!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:14.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HF9F94A&}That is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:22.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HF9F94A&}Purupuru pururin pururin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:24.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I saw Misaki and talked to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:25.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HF9F94A&}Purupuru pururin purupururin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.48,0:20:28.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told her the truth about\nmy being hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:28.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HF9F94A&}Purupuru pururin pururin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:33.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to admit that I didn't think we could\nmake a decent game in ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HF9F94A&}Purupuru pururin pururin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:37.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's all because of the delay in your\nscript writing part, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:38.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HF9F94A&}Purupuru pururin purupururin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:39.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not going to quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:41.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HF9F94A&}Purupuru pururin pururin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:43.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've collected sound effects for free\nand even programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:45.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as we have the script,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:48.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we should be able to make it happen\nif we work intensively!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:50.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as we have the script!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:53.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:57.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't wanna quit either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:01.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My promise to Misaki is over with, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:04.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, that's exactly why we should take our time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:07.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and make something good without\nworrying about a deadline!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:10.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:13.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the story for the game\nthat I've come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:16.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wrote down some characters' names too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:19.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're nothing like the ones in the games\nyou'd see at the store though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:26.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm a loser and I admit that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:29.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm just an unemployed hikikomoro man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:33.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if I can finish making this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:36.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel like I could be a better man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:38.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:45.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's make it! Let's make our game!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:47.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:59.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFDFBF5&\shad0\3c&H000000&\fscx187.5\fscy192.5\pos(194,92)\bord2.3}Episode 05
