Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:15.58,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Ababa, ababa, ababa, dancing baby human!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.60,0:22:23.03,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,When we were born naked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:24.54,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,When we were born naked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.54,0:22:25.97,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,We were all loved equally
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:27.47,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Just as it's supposed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.47,0:22:29.01,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,But why, as life goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:30.34,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,But why, as life goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:32.11,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Each destiny takes a different path
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.11,0:22:33.41,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,It's almost cruel
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:35.05,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Some can look at other's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.05,0:22:36.48,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,While others can't
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:37.95,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Some get to learn love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.95,0:22:39.42,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,While others don't
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:41.02,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,If that's how it is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:42.45,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd rather be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.45,0:22:45.59,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,A baby, a baby human till I die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:51.56,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,"Oh, what an adorable baby!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.56,0:22:54.53,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,"I just want to love you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:56.03,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Just like I planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.03,0:22:57.57,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,It worked perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.57,0:23:00.47,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,The baby she is holding is really a baby human
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.47,0:23:02.07,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,"Ababa!" I snicker to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:03.47,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiding in my pretended innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.47,0:23:05.11,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so easy to be a baby human
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.11,0:23:06.44,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,So you should be one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:08.11,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Ababa, ababa! Dance, multiply
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:09.25,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,And take it to space!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:10.01,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,To Mars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:10.78,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,To Saturn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:11.52,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,To the galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.52,0:23:12.18,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:13.72,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Baby human!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:14.49,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:16.18,nhked,Comment,0,0,0,,Baby human!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:32.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You should definitely play it too, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:34.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is looking down on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.94,0:23:36.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How am I gonna get home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.84,0:23:39.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next episode,\N"Welcome to the Classroom!"
